All Implemented Interfaces:
NodeVisitor<ExprNode,JavaExpr>
public class TranslateToJavaExprVisitor
extends AbstractExprNodeVisitor<JavaExpr>

Visitor for translating a Soy expression (in the form of an ExprNode) into an equivalent Java expression.

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).
